parameters:
Guardian of the Summoned "…Oh... you... are not from the people of
Kuseshi..."
Kru "Yes... I come from the outside world..."

Guardian of the Summoned "You intend to... steal the power of the
priestesses..."
Kru "No... I have no such intention..."

Guardian of the Summoned "I won't allow it! I will protect them! I won't
let you lay a finger on our priestesses!"
洞窟戦闘カット
Umi "They're coming..."
Kru "Ah! Umi, it's dangerous, stay back!"
Umi "No, I'm worried about you being alone. Umi will fight too."
Kru "Umi... then let's finish this quickly!"
Guardian of the Summoned "Ah... you are... of Lady Kuseshirei's..."
Umi "About Umi?"
Guardian of the Summoned "Beyond here... you must not... go..."
A
Kru: "Phew... That was a pretty tough enemy..."
Umi: "Haa... We can finally go back..."
Kru: "Hahaha! Thanks for guiding the way! I'm beat."
Umi: "Tired... But..."
Kru: "But?"
Umi: "Sometimes... adventure can be nice."

Kru: "Pfft... Hahahaha! That's true! Adventure can be nice once in a
while!"
Umi: "Hmm... Why are you laughing?"
Kru: "Well... It was unexpected, I guess."
Umi: "That's true... It's not like me to say something like that..."
Kru: "Indeed."
Grrrrr...
Kru: "That sound just now..."

Umi: "...What is it with you. Are you hungry? You're such a hopeless case.
Let's hurry back and eat."
Kru: "Eh, that noise was, you know"
Umi: "Come on... Let's go back. We're going back right now."

Kru: "...Alright, alright... Umi-san is hungry, after all. Let's head back
quickly."
アイキャッチ1
アイキャッチ1タイトル
We hurried back to the village...

Along the way, Umi wanted to take breaks several times, but I refused
because monsters were swarming all around us.

I couldn't tell if Umi lacked crisis management skills, or if she was just
too hungry and acting silly, but she kept making selfish requests and then
looked dissatisfied.
But somehow, her opening up like that made me happy...
